::Zardus::

Zardus looks at Soundwave as the bot explains his mission. He opens his mouth 
to reply as a new bot rushes in, Zardus jumping to his feet, his hand on his 
gun. He glances from Soundwave to the new bot, wondering how they knew each 
other.

"I am Zardus," he says to the new bot, "I assume you're joining the Alliance?"
